item.description: Biography I am a fourth year undergraduate student pursuing B.Tech - M.Tech(Dual Degree) in Computer Science at Indian Institute of Technology, Kanpur. I am highly interested in the field of Knowledge Compilation, Cyber Security and AI. In past, I have done courses and projects in Computer Systems Security, Machine Learning, Computer Vision, Data Structures and Algorithms, Operating Systems, Compilers and Database Management Systems. I interned at Microsoft in the last summer.
